By: Rûmî
---
The gnostics are the laziest folk in the two worlds, because they get
their harvest without ploughing.

They have made laziness their prop (and rely upon it) since God is
working for them.

The vulgar do not see God’s working and (therefore) never rest from
toil at morn or eve.
